{ Parting with the light-squared Bishop speeds up White's development but now Black will dominate on the light squares. }
9... Bxd7 10. Ne3 Nh5
{ Played only once but Black's idea is crystal clear - we want to put the Knight on f4 or play ... Qh4+ with deadly threats. The other option is ... f5. }
